Class MemberList

fitnessclub.MemberList
public class MemberList extends Object

    • compare

      private int compare(Member member1, Member member2, int mode)
      Helper method for insertion sort, compares two members given a mode of comparison.
      Parameters:
      member1 - the first member being compared
      member2 - the second member being compared
      mode - an int which determines by which attribute the members will be compared.
      Returns:
      returns a negative value if 1st attribute comes before, positive if it comes after, 0 if equal.
